title: Iya Villania, Drew Arellano welcome baby no. 5
creator: Christina Alpad
description: MANILA, Philippines — Celebrity couple Iya Villania and Drew Arellano welcomed their fifth child, Anya Love, on Tuesday morning.The couple shared the news on their respective Instagram accounts.Arellano posted a photo of Anya Love, detailing that she was born at 10:52 a.m. on Feb. 11.Meanwhile, in a series of Instagram Stories, Villania shared that she experienced prodromal labor for the first time prior to giving birth.According healthline.com, prodromal labor is the labor that "stops before fully active labor begins." It is often referred as "false labor" because it does not necessarily lead directly to birth.Fifteen hours later, the fifth-time mom said she had a swift delivery. "Got to the hospital at 10 a.m., by 10:52 a.m., baby's out!" she wrote.Anya Love is the couple's second daughter. They have four other children — Primo (8) Leon (6), Alana (4), and Astro (2). In 2024, Villania and Arellano their 10th wedding anniversary.
